room_title: Escape room "Museum of Terror" by Puzzled Escape Rooms in Fargo
room_address: 114 Broadway N Suite L1 Fargo, ND 58102
room_description: C J Kask was a world-famous explorer from the early 1900's who collected dark antiquities from around the world and displayed them in his many Museums of Terror. One of the stars of the collection is the body Prince Zoric, a vampire. During the grand opening, one of the guests removed the stake from Prince Zoric and hid it. Your job is to locate the stake somewhere in the room and lay Prince Zoric back to rest before he wakes!
